"""
parameter golf submission: int6 STE + NorMuon + NTK rope extrapolation + SWA + sliding window

- int6 fake quantization w/ STE during training
- fp16 passthrough on embedding (no quant penalty on most sensitive tensor)
- 3x wider MLP (1536 hidden) enabled by int6 compression savings
- NorMuon optimizer (row-normalized Newton-Schulz updates)
- NTK-aware RoPE extrapolation: train at 1024, eval at 2048 for more context
- sliding window eval w/ stride=64
- stochastic weight averaging during warmdown
- optimizer tuning: momentum 0.99, lower LRs, longer warmdown
"""

